      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Identify and quantify differentially methylated bases or regions between sample groups using statistical tests that account for methylation heterogeneity and overdispersion. This skill applies Fisher's exact test or logistic regression to bisulfite sequencing methylation calls, f",
