      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "DMCs/DMRs can be visualized as horizontal barplots showing percentage of hyper- and hypo-methylated bases/regions out of covered cytosines over all chromosomes (Figure 5a). We observed higher levels of hypomethylation than hypermethylation in the breast cancer cell lines... methyl Kit can output bedgraph tracks (Figure 5b) for use with the UCSC Genome Browser or Integrated Genome Viewer.",
      "asbval:note": "Confirmed. Paper describes both barplot and bedGraph visualization outputs.",
