      "asbval:note": "Paper performs annotation of DMCs/DMRs with gene parts (promoters, exons, introns, intergenic) and CpG islands/shores using methylKit's built-in annotation functions, NOT genomation's annotateWithGeneParts() or annotateWithFeatureFlank(). The functional capability is present but the specific tool names are incorrect.",
