      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Here, we describe an R package, methyl Kit, that rapidly analyzes genome-wide cytosine epigenetic profiles... methyl Kit is dependent on Bioconductor packages such as Genomic Ranges and its objects are coercible to Genomic Ranges objects and regular R data structures such as data frames via provided convenience functions.",
      "asbval:note": "R is confirmed as the environment for methylKit and Bioconductor packages (including Genomic Ranges), but genomation and GenomicFeatures are not mentioned in the paper.",
